-> launch vm 
-> verify the network interfaces (private and public addresses)
-> if dhcp not set, edit network interfaces
auto xxx
iface xxx inet dhcp 
-> install ssh
-> /etc/ssh/sshd_config - set PermiRootLogin: yes 
-> ssh-copy-id of root 
-> set PermitRootLogin: prohibit-password (good practice) 
-> Launch playbook 
-> The wordpress site is at https://vm_ip
